    {
      "num": 2,
      "geez": "ወበህየ፡ ርኢኩ፡ ኅቡኣተ፡ ነጐድጓድ፡ ወሶበ፡ ይደቅቅ፡ በመልዕልተ፡ ሰማይ፡ ቃሎሙ፡ ይሰማዕ፡ ወማኅደራተ፡ የብስ፡ አስተርአየኒ፡ ወቃል፡ ነጐድጓድ፡ ለሰላም፡ ወለበረከት፡ ወለእመ፡ ለረጊም፡ በቃለ፡ እግዚአ፡ መናፍስት።",
      "translation": "And there I saw the secrets of the thunder, and how when it resounds above in the heaven, the sound thereof is heard, and he caused me to see the judgements executed on the earth, whether they be for well-being and blessing, or for a curse according to the word of the Lord of Spirits.",
